headline: Midstream/MLP Q3 2025 Buybacks Surged To Record Level
summary: Quarterly equity repurchases for midstream MLPs and corps reached a new high watermark. Here we take a look at 3Q25 repurchase activity and how record buybacks are amplifying total return.

headline: Targa Resources to acquire Stakeholder Midstream in $1.25bn deal
summary: Stakeholder Midstream offers natural gas gathering, treating and processing services, as well as crude oil gathering and storage services in the Permian Basin.

headline: Targa Resources (TRGP): Exploring Valuation as Investors Reassess Midstream Momentum
summary: Targa Resources (TRGP) stock has been moving steadily, drawing attention as investors weigh the company’s latest performance against broader energy sector trends.
